These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle, rat
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the rat is the person driving the roller##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Pet   | lizard | turtle | rat   |
| Transport      | trike    | motorbike  | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, ferret, rat
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the bike is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Pet      | ferret | guinea-pig     | rat      |
| Transport   | bike | taxi | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, subway, helicopter
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, epic, superhero
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Transport   | tram | helicopter  | subway       |
| Movie-Genre       | crime     | epic | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, roller, airplane
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, red, orange
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Transport    | airplane    | roller     | bike |
| Color   | orange | chestnut | red     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, horror
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, may, august
1. the person who's birthday is in may is the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Movie-Genre         | satire | mystery     | horror |
| Birthday   | august        | march | may    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, thai
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, thriller, western
1. the dutch is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the malaysian is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the thai is the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Nationality        | thai | dutch      | malaysian  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire       | thriller | western |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, kiwi, orange
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, comedy, spy
1. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
2. the person eating kiwi is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Food   | orange      | pomegranate     | kiwi    |
| Movie-Genre           | sports | spy | comedy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, climbing, rowing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, dubstep
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Sport    | rowing | ice-hockey | climbing      |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | dubstep | hip-hop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
City: colone, hannover, marseilles
House: townhouse, farmhouse, colonial
1. the townhouse house is the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| City   | marseilles | hannover | colone  |
| House     | colonial     | townhouse      | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, grey, brown
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, camping, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Color      | pink   | grey    | brown    |
| Hobby   | camping | board-games | drawing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, june, april
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, vegafina, bongani
1. the person who's birthday is in april is the game-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Birthday   | january | april   | june  |
| Cigar   | bongani    | game | vegafina |

 #################################

 
