.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, dog, horse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, zinnia, aconite
1. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Pet      | goat  | horse | dog  |
| Flower   | zinnia | aconite   | sunflower |

