.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, electronic, gospel
3 different games are played: backgammon, domino, canasta
1. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | hip-hop | gospel    |
| Game        | backgammon    | canasta | domino |

