2. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsorchid is the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Color           | green | ivory | brown |
| Flower   | daffodil  | orchid      | rose |

