.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, fantasy, satire
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, filmmaking, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Movie-Genre    | fantasy | satire   | thriller        |
| Hobby   | filmmaking    | skydiving | puzzles |

